Thanksgiving Point is a 501(c)(3) nonprofit farm, garden, and museum complex in Lehi, Utah, United States. Its venues include the Museum of Ancient Life, Farm Country, the Museum of Natural Curiosity, and Ashton Gardens. In 2018, the fifth venue, the Butterfly Biosphere will open as well.
Other attractions include the Thanksgiving Point Golf Course, Harvest restaurant, Tower Deli, and Brick Canvas spa.


